    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that's practically perfect and ready for a new home, this is the one. I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have, so don't be a stranger!",
      "price": 43500.0,
