    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level specimen featuring a high-revving, naturally aspirated power plant with individual throttle bodies and optimized valve timing maps. The drivetrain is anchored by a precision six-speed close-ratio transmission and a torque-biasing limited-slip differential, ensuring linear power delivery. The chassis retains factory-spec torsional rigidity with zero subframe fatigue, supported by a meticulously maintained multi-link suspension geometry. This vehicle exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders, no evidence of thermal cycling fatigue on gaskets, and an immaculate undercarriage. A turn-key investment for the purist seeking mechanical perfection and original factory tolerances.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
