    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained by a single enthusiast owner. Finished in its original factory paint, the exterior is absolutely flawless\u2014free of rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections\u2014and has been protected with a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in time-capsule condition; the premium leather upholstery shows zero bolster wear, the dash is crack-free, and it still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with every scheduled maintenance performed ahead of time at the dealership. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line, with tight steering, smooth shifts, and a quiet, powerful engine. Included are all original keys, the factory window sticker, and a complete stack of service receipts. If you are looking for the finest example currently on the market, this is it.",
      "price": 48500.0,
